    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a YANG data model and associated mechanism that enable adaptive subscription to a publisher's event streams. The periodic update interval for the event streams can be set adaptively. Applying these elements allows servers to automatically adjust the rate and volume of telemetry traffic sent from a publisher to receivers.</t>
